    "description": "作为一家尖端基因研究实验室的顶级科学家，你要争分夺秒地解决人口爆炸带来的温饱问题。你的团队超越了伦理底线，试图通过基因编辑技术培育出一种新型牲畜，其生长速度是普通动物的100倍。<br><br>但是，某次实验受到了神秘干扰，大量的病毒性细胞应运而生，它们疯狂扩散，吞噬沿途的一切，并进化成了一种恐怖的怪物。你必须运用自己的科学经验，了解这种怪物的行为规律，并利用其弱点奋力逃到安全地带。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >未知敌人</h2>这个面目可憎的怪物由肉身和触手组成，嗜食有机物，能不断进化和适应环境，并野蛮蔓延，吞噬所到之处的一切事物。利用你能找到的所有工具，切断怪物的触手，瞄准其弱点并阻止其生长。在怪物生长变异成更可怕的东西之前，逃离该楼层。<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1808160/extras/22c8eb9504620a17f1996c28550e1ab2.poster.avif?t=1757409761\" width=600 height=140 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1808160/extras/22c8eb9504620a17f1996c28550e1ab2.webm?t=1757409761\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1808160/extras/22c8eb9504620a17f1996c28550e1ab2.mp4?t=1757409761\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >组队逃生</h2>你可以选择在本地合作模式中与朋友一起组队，最多可有4名玩家一同尝试逃离实验室。请谨慎选择任务和角色，并互相照应——团队必须齐心协力，才能在触手横行的地狱中生存下来。<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1808160/extras/f38438279928a7a18f52b95372480632.poster.avif?t=1757409761\" width=600 height=140 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1808160/extras/f38438279928a7a18f52b95372480632.webm?t=1757409761\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1808160/extras/f38438279928a7a18f52b95372480632.mp4?t=1757409761\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >巧妙逃生</h2>利用你的科学知识重新利用实验室设备和系统，减缓怪物的生长速度或令其转移注意力。操纵实验室的布局，紧上门并开辟新的路线，以阻止怪物的蔓延。临时拼凑实验武器或创造新技术，在瞬息万变的环境中，为逃生而战。<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1808160/extras/80ead221927b3bacda1a7c3ef0d8e922.poster.avif?t=1757409761\" width=600 height=140 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1808160/extras/80ead221927b3bacda1a7c3ef0d8e922.webm?t=1757409761\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1808160/extras/80ead221927b3bacda1a7c3ef0d8e922.mp4?t=1757409761\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >艰难抉择</h2>每个房间都会给你带来全新惊喜和艰难抉择。是在怪物发现你之前偷偷溜走，还是设置陷阱扭转战局风向？是拯救一名科学家以解锁新设备，还是减少损失，争分夺秒地冲向出口？但务必要小心——即使是你的科学家同事也有可能在不知情的情况下，携带伺机释放自己的休眠生长体……<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1808160/extras/64e4780fad8e5502784bb111ed9f902e.poster.avif?t=1757409761\" width=600 height=140 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1808160/extras/64e4780fad8e5502784bb111ed9f902e.webm?t=1757409761\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1808160/extras/64e4780fad8e5502784bb111ed9f902e.mp4?t=1757409761\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >随机应变</h2>每条逃生路径上都有不同的危险和不同的奖励，明智地选择自己的逃生路线，始终领先怪物一步。每次游戏中都会面临截然不同的布局，但你会了解到更多实验室的秘密，以及如何利用这些来智胜敌人。<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1808160/extras/3cd58ea36b6cbf3618941aacaa959477.poster.avif?t=1757409761\" width=600 height=140 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1808160/extras/3cd58ea36b6cbf3618941aacaa959477.webm?t=1757409761\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1808160/extras/3cd58ea36b6cbf3618941aacaa959477.mp4?t=1757409761\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
